               <msContents>
                  <summary>Folio 1 is blank.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="2v" to="20r">2v-20r</locus>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s10IHA">قران, Third ǧuz’ (3/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#2v">-2v</locus>تلك الرسل فضلنا بعضهم على بعض منهم من كلم \ الله \ ورفع بعذهم درجات<note>The word الله is written between the two first lines. </note>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#20r">-20r</locus>ولو افتدى به اولئك لهم عذاب اليم وما لهم من ناصرين</explicit>
                     <note>2:253-3:91. Copied by the same hand as EMIP02749, EMIP02750 and EMIP02752. Red triple dots as verse markers. Interlinear taǧwīd markers in red. Heading of sūra in red on fol. 9v. Ǧuz' marker in red (fol. 2v), ḥizb marker in red (fol. 11r), niṣf ḥizb marker in red (fol. 15v). Some additions and corrections in the margins.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
